# 📌 Backend Summary

The backend of **SB Stocks** is developed using **Node.js**, **Express.js**, **MongoDB**, and **Mongoose** following the **MVC (Model-View-Controller)** architecture. The project is organized into Config, Controllers, Middlewares, Models, Routes, and Root Files, where each component performs a dedicated responsibility. This modular architecture improves code readability, maintainability, scalability, testing, and future development while supporting secure authentication, paper trading, portfolio management, and real-time stock market operations.
